main event: A round, bright silver object approximately 50-75 feet in diameter was observed hovering over a neighbor's house before rapidly disappearing in a southerly direction.
interesting points: The object was first observed hovering over a neighbor's house for a few minutes.
The object then abruptly changed direction and disappeared rapidly in a southerly direction.
No sound was heard from the object.
The sighting was reported to the local police department.
The report does not contain any photographs, only a description of the observed object.
